# Module: Core Library (packages/excalidraw)

## Context

This is the main React/TypeScript library consumed by external apps. It must be stable, typed, and side-effect safe.

## Rule

- Maintain strict TypeScript typing (no any)
- Avoid breaking public API
- Prefer pure functions and predictable behavior
- Do not introduce app-specific logic
- Keep components reusable and composable
- Avoid direct DOM manipulation unless necessary

## How to verify

- Search for any usage — should be minimal or zero
- Ensure exported APIs are stable and documented
- Confirm no references to app-specific modules (excalidraw-app)
